203
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:04,920
This is not something

204
00:14:04,920 --> 00:14:07,440
a common cultivator would use.

205
00:14:07,440 --> 00:14:09,040
I'm afraid that

206
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:12,720
it's something introduced from foreign regions.

207
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:14,600
From foreign regions?

208
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:16,520
Someone in the Ghost Market

209
00:14:16,520 --> 00:14:17,800
might know

210
00:14:17,800 --> 00:14:19,800
where this thing is from.

211
00:14:19,800 --> 00:14:20,840
Master.

212
00:14:20,840 --> 00:14:22,840
