241
00:15:28,160 --> 00:15:30,960
with an enemy in the dark

242
00:15:30,960 --> 00:15:33,160
to see who can gain control

243
00:15:33,160 --> 00:15:36,000
one step ahead.

244
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:37,600
If the case

245
00:15:37,600 --> 00:15:39,360
of the Jinxiu Workshop

246
00:15:39,360 --> 00:15:41,560
